      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          3. WHEN: It's going down <a target='blank' href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&dates=20170716/20170717&location=Granby+Ranch+Granby+CO&text=Johnson-Grever+Wedding&details=We+are+so+excited+to+see+you+in+Colorado!!%0A%0A--%0Ahttp://www.paulandtahra.party" >July 16, 2017!</a>
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <%= image_tag("july-16.jpg", class: 'overview') %>
          <div class='item-text'>
            <p><a target='blank' href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&dates=20170716/20170717&location=Granby+Ranch+Granby+CO&text=Johnson-Grever+Wedding&details=We+are+so+excited+to+see+you+in+Colorado!!%0A%0A--%0Ahttp://www.paulandtahra.party">Save it your Google Calendar!!!</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          4. WHERE: Granby Ranch, Granby Colorado
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <iframe
            width="100%"
            height="470"
            frameborder="0" style="border:0"
