          <div class='item-text'>
            <p><b><a targe='_blank' href='http://www.granbyranch.com/'>Granby Ranch</a></b> is a small ski resort during the winter and a mountain bikers dream during the summer. It's  located just 90 miles west of Denver and only 20 miles west of Winter Park.</p>
            <p>Call 888-850-4615 or email reservationcenter@granbyranch.com for golf, fly fishing, mountain biking, and lodging.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          5. WHY: Because ... we are the Bones!
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <%= image_tag("the_bones.jpg", class: 'overview') %>
          <div class='item-text'>
            <p>Paul and Tahra met freshman year of college at American University on 4 North in Anderson Hall. They were more of acquaintances in college and years after. Tahra enjoyed visiting Paul at Grand Central long before they started dating. On her 25th birthday, Paul iced Tahra from behind the bar... and only 3 years later did they go on their first "date" at Meridian Pint. Only, they didn't know it was a date at the time. After a lovely evening of beers and sweet potato wedges, Paul kissed Tahra and it was like (FILL IN THE BLANK!). They then started a fun relationship of dating- which included trapeze lessons, Easter egg hunts, indoor skydiving, beer tastings and eventually- joined a soccer team together. It didn't take long for Tahra and Paul to know they had met their soulmate. It took two years for their friends to start calling them "The Bones".</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          6. HOW: Via Chairlift!
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <%= image_tag("chair_lift.jpg", class: 'overview') %>
          <div class='item-text'>
            <p><b>Yes</b> – there will be a chairlift taking you up to the ceremony site! Don’t worry- if you are afraid of heights- we will get you a shuttle.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          7. Altitude is REAL
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <%= image_tag("altitude.png", class: 'overview') %>
          <div class='item-text'>
            <p><b>The wedding will take place above 8,000 ft</b></p>
            <p>How can you avoid altitude sickness one may ask?</p>
            <ol>
              <li>Drink water!</li>
              <li>Drink water!</li>
              <li>Drink water!</li>
              <li>An aspirin or two may also help if feel a headache coming on.</li>
              <li>Drink water!</li>
            </ol>     
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          8. The Weather is Cray in Colorado! 
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <iframe width="100%" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZpBEKGuVkRQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <div class='item-text'>
            <p>You may need 50 SPF sunblock AND a rain coat within 20 minutes of each other.</p>
            <p>The sun is VERY strong- even if you don’t feel it, you are getting some rays. Please consider wearing moisturizer with SPF or sunblock.</p>
            <p>Summer afternoon storms are normal- they come through relatively quickly- so be prepared with a rain coat!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='row'>
        <div class='col-xs-12 list-items'>
          9. Rocky Mountain National Park is 20 miles away!
        </div>
        <div class='col-xs-12'>
          <%= image_tag("rocky-mountain-national-park.jpg", class: 'overview') %>
          <div class='item-text'>
          <p>If you have time to make this event a mini vacation- it is absolutely worth it exploring the mountains and lakes in the area!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
